extendedInfo.description: Get a laugh every time your phone rings, now at 50% off! You get more than two thousand fun ringtones for one low price. What do we mean by "one price?" Simple, after you buy the app, you can download as many ringtones as you want for NO CHARGE! Zip, zero, nada.Examples include:"Warning! An idiot is calling.""That smoking hot babe with the long legs is calling. You better pick up!""Miss High Maintenance is calling you...AGAIN!""Your ex-wife is calling. Time to hit the ignore button, isn't it?!""Your boyfriend is calling. Well, aren't you the lucky one!"...and thousands more!Quickly scroll through the list of tones. Touch a tone name to listen to a short preview. If you like what you hear, download the entire tone -- up to 30 seconds each. Download as many as you like for no additional charge!Use the app to listen to downloaded tones, or to set your default ringtone. Use the Android contact manager to set specific ringtones for your friends or co-workers.Features include:- Unlimited ringtone downloads for no charge (data fees may apply to your calling plan)- Instantly install ringtones directly to your Android- High-quality, custom tones you can get nowhere elseMEDIA CARD REQUIRED TO SAVE RINGTONESHere's a few ringtones you get:Air HeadAngel EyesBaby reviews.title: Plentiful selection of nick names columned voice selection variety.
reviews.comment: Simple voice; too professional sounding and dull where creativity could have made these phrases over the top and also could have made this app great! Plentiful variety of nick names/titles (2500); this apps voices just dont have the variety in their sounds..in my opinion. If you take time to go through the whole list i do recommend it as there are many that do fit with the voices that i will utilize!
